    "body" : "<a href=\"https://github.com/fuiny/binarydoc-docker-compose\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">binarydoc</a> is a <b>Free</b> tool which can generate diagram from the Java <code>bytecode</code> directly, it can generate <code>UML hierarchy diagrams</code>, <code>UML class diagram</code>, <code>Class Cross-reference diagram</code>, Java code <code>Control flow diagram</code>, Java code <code>UML sequence diagrams</code>, etc. There is a sample UML diagram for the class <a href=\"https://openjdk.binarydoc.org/net.java/openjdk/13.0/classfile?classfilelocation=java.net.datagramsocket\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">java.net.DatagramSocket</a>"
