    "body" : "<p>How about the <a href=\"http://www.ejb3.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Omondo</a> Plugin for Eclipse. I have used it and I find it to be quite useful. Although if you are generating diagrams for large sources, you might have to start Eclipse with more memory.</p>\n"
